{"tid":106919,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"專家指侵收緊合法移民福利會令百萬美國人挨餓","createTime":"2017-02-04T05:23:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T10:26:43.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a494c0bf2eb7699434a3c61cc1c1f45ef083f86","tid":106919,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:23:07.000Z","msg":"Millions of Americans could go hungry if President Trump moves forward with a draft executive order that restricts the welfare benefits available to immigrants, according to experts in immigration law.<br />\n<br />\nThat&rsquo;s because the order would restrict access to needs-based nutrition programs, like SNAP and WIC, that are currently accessed by millions of first-generation immigrants both for themselves and on behalf of their second-generation, citizen children.<br />\n<br />\nAccording to a recent analysis by the National Academies of Sciences, 45.3 percent of all immigrant-headed households with children use a food assistance program. Eighty-eight percentof all children living with immigrant parents are themselves U.S. citizens.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/wonk/wp/2017/02/03/trumps-draft-plan-to-cut-off-food-stamps-for-immigrants-could-cause-some-u-s-citizens-to-go-hungry/?utm_term=.0e6d6c7ec92b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnews%2Fwonk%2Fwp%2F2017%2F02%2F03%2Ftrumps-draft-plan-to-cut-off-food-stamps-for-immigrants-could-cause-some-u-s-citizens-to-go-hungry%2F%3Futm_term%3D.0e6d6c7ec92b&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9FzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=f96b2da3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/wonk/wp/2017/02/03/trumps-draft-plan-to-cut-off-food-stamps-for-immigrants-could-cause-some-u-s-citizens-to-go-hungry/?utm_term=.0e6d6c7ec92b</a>"},{"pid":"ee060faf44177e7974ceb10249c97011f0eb5187","tid":106919,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:25:26